column44:
Motor control is based on proportional control. Using: float rad = _angle * PI / 180.0;

    float t1 = sin(rad + PI/4);
    float t2 = sin(rad - PI/4);
    float t3 = sin(rad + 3*PI/4);
    float t4 = sin(rad - 3*PI/4);
